ËÆÐZ<?php exit; ?>a:6:{s:10:"last_error";s:0:"";s:10:"last_query";s:223:"SELECT   wpw6_posts.* FROM wpw6_posts  WHERE 1=1  AND wpw6_posts.post_name = 'sam-claflin-career-upcoming-projects-personal-life-achievements-net-worth' AND wpw6_posts.post_type = 'post'  ORDER BY wpw6_posts.post_date DESC ";s:11:"last_result";a:1:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"1500";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2018-03-01 22:22:29";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2018-03-01 16:37:29";s:12:"post_content";s:6505:"<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>Sam Claflin</em></strong> is not a new name in the entertainment industry, he is the one who also started his career from television series and made it into the world ofÂ  big screen. Claflin is talented and knows what to deliver when he is into the character so Sam has been able to grow followers during his journey in the entertainment world.</p>
&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>Samuel George Claflin</em></strong> was born on 27 June 1986, Ipswich and brought up in Norwich, London. He was third child to an <strong><em>accountant</em></strong> father Mark Claflin and <strong><em>education assistance</em></strong> mother Sue Claflin. Sam had an early interest in football when he was a child and was registered in Norwich City football club but his ankle injury prevented him from playing football.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Career </strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Sam Claflin made his career debut through the television mini-series in 2010. In 2011 he acted in <strong><em>Pirates of the Caribbean: On strange Tides,</em></strong> one of the famous American movie as <strong><em>Philip Swift. </em></strong>Â He continued journey into television series too, after his debut in miniseries 2010 he did some of the television films <strong><em>The Lost Future (2010)</em></strong>, <strong><em>United (2011)</em></strong> and <strong><em>Mary and Martha(2013).</em></strong></p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1506" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/tumblr_mr8dhsAZf51sd8ra8o3_1280-300x184.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="328" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Sam really has an extremely good career in movie industry since 2011 after he was cast into the <strong><em>Pirates of the Caribbean: On strange Tides. </em></strong>In 2012 he featured in <strong><em>Snow Whites and Huntsman. </em></strong>Sam uplifted his career through the movie <strong><em>The Hunger Games: Catching Fire (2013) </em></strong>where he portrayed the role of <strong><em>Finnick Odaira. </em></strong>In the following year, Sam came up with four movies <strong><em>The Quite Ones (2014),</em></strong> <strong><em>The Riot Club (2014),</em></strong> <strong><em>Love, Rosie (2014)</em></strong> along with the sequel of hunger games <strong><em>The Hunger Games: Mockingjay Â Part-1(2014). </em></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">In the year 2015, the sequel of <strong><em>The Hunger Games: Mockingjay Part-2 </em></strong>was released in which the character <strong><em>Finnick Odaira</em></strong> was admired by most of the viewers. Similarly in the following year the sequel of <strong><em>Snow Whites and Huntsman</em></strong> was released as <strong><em>The Huntsman: Winterâ€™s War (2016).</em></strong></p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1507" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/me-before-you-300x171.jpg" alt="" width="534" height="304" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Sam has delivered immensely good acting skills into his romantic movies <strong><em>Me Before You (2016) </em></strong>where he was cast along with <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/emilia-clarke-career-upcoming-projects-achievements-personal-life-net-worth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Emilia Clarke</a> as William Traynor and <strong><em>My Cousin Rachel (2017) </em></strong>with Rachel Weise. He has been delivering best into any character he plays which can be seen in British comedy war drama <strong><em>Their Finest (2017).</em></strong> <strong><em>Journeyâ€™s Ends (2017)</em></strong> is his another acclaimed movie released where Sam Claflin acted as Captain Stanhope.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Upcoming Projects</strong></p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1508" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Sam-Claflin-06-300x174.png" alt="" width="536" height="311" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Sam Claflin is currently busy shooting his upcoming movie <strong><em>Adrift </em></strong>and he has been confirmed to join <strong><em>Jamie Dornan</em></strong> for action and thriller movie <strong>Borderland</strong>. <strong>The Nightingale</strong> is another upcoming movie set to release in 2018.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Â </strong><strong>Personal Life</strong></p>
Sam was interested in playing football in his early days and he still loves watching them. He started dating <strong><em>Laura Haddock</em></strong> and extended their relationship by getting married to each other in 2013.Laura and Sam wound up as a pleased guardian to a son and they are expecting a second child soon. <strong><em>Laura Haddock</em></strong> and Sam both are very private about their family. He also has a brother named Joseph Clafin, an actor who has acted in the movie Da Vinciâ€™s Demons.

<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1509" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/tmp_PeeiSA_9ec041bfb93c8aef_1-300x188.jpg" alt="" width="534" height="334" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Â </strong><strong>Achievements</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Sam Claflin has been nominated into different category and won <strong><em>Glamour Awards </em></strong>for <strong><em>Man of the year</em></strong>. With his long career he has grown with lots of fan following with 2.8 million followers in Instagram and 1.01 followers on twitter. The <a href="https://twitter.com/samclaflin?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor" target="_blank" rel="noopener">twitter</a> and <a href="https://www.instagram.com/mrsamclaflin/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a> handle of Sam claflin is <a href="https://twitter.com/samclaflin?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@samclaflin</a> and <a href="https://www.instagram.com/mrsamclaflin/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@mrsamclaflin.</a></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Net Worth </strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Sam Claflin has made it all from the movies and his net worth is reported to be $6 million.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">This stylist actor is smart enough to act on any character, so we are pretty sure he will not be disappointing us in coming future. With his upcoming movies he will definitely grow some more followers.</p>
